#### 4. Mystery Guest (testsmells.org Smell #2)

**Method:** `ImportOrders_FromCsv_ParsesCorrectly` (line 139)

```csharp
File.ReadAllText(@"C:\TestData\orders.csv")
```

**Problem:** Depends on an external file at a hard-coded Windows path. Fails on CI, Linux, or any machine without that file. Environment coupling is the top cause of "works on my machine" flakiness.

**Fix:** Inline the test data or use an embedded resource:

```csharp
[TestMethod]
public void ImportOrders_FromCsv_ParsesCorrectly()
{
    var processor = new OrderProcessor(_db, _email, _inventory);
    var csv = "SKU-1,2,19.99\nSKU-2,1,49.99\nSKU-3,1,10.00\nSKU-4,3,5.00\nSKU-5,1,75.00";

    var orders = processor.ImportOrders(csv);

    Assert.AreEqual(5, orders.Count);
}
```

